<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<base href="/">
<title>Ipefix Payment Solution</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/registered.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="boldi light-blue">Ipefix Payment Solution</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form action="#">
                <div class="col-md-6 border-right">
                    <div class="pull-right content-left">
                        <h2 class="dark-blue boldi">Oup's ...</h2>
                        <h4 class="result mid-red">Une erreur est survenue  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-warning-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span></h4>
                        <p>Vous trouverez le détail de l'erreur sur la partie droite de la page.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 border-left">
                    <div class="pull-left content-right">
                        <p class="detail">
                            <strong><u>Détail de l'erreur:</u></strong><br>
                            <code class="code">
                                {% if error %}
                                    {{ error }}
                                {% else %}
                                    Une erreur inattendue est survenu.
                                {% endif %}
                            </code>
                            <br><br>Vous pouvez contacter le support technique à l'adresse <a href="mailto:info@ipefix.com">info@ipefix.com</a> en mentionnent l'erreur.
                            <br><br>
                            Cordialement, l'équipe d'Ipefix.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="images/powered_by_stripe.png" alt="powered-by-stripe" class="poweredby">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>